name: Alpha Series 0n1 #6459
description: Loki went missing on one of his adventures for a while.  When he returned he had a new friend.  Red skinned and red masked, Loki's mustachioed new pal loves some slicing and dicing and acts as a bodyguard to our tricky old friend. A lot less people seem willing to go toe to toe with old Loki these days…
